name: Vermont Center for Geographic Information, Cemeteries, Vermont, 2001
description:
Abstract: The BasemapLandmarks_CEMETERY point layer contains cemeteries in the state of Vermont.  The data is based on VTrans Town Highway Maps.  Some points have been moved to match RF24000 USGS topo cemetery locations.
    Purpose: Location of cemeteries in the state of Vermont.
Please search Vermont-GIS for more local level GIS data for Vermont.
